<div class="lead">
  <div class="lead-card">
    <p>Most "AI receptionists" do one trick. 406 Front Desk runs the <strong>entire front desk</strong> on one platform — capturing customers, booking them in, and following up — without you touching any software. We build it, train it on your business, and keep it running.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:12px; font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-muted);">Answering, booking, follow-up, and payments come standard in every plan. Features marked <span class="tag tag-addon">Add-on</span> are priced separately, by scope — see <a href="/pricing/" style="color:var(--accent-dark); font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;">pricing</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

