        <div class="feat-title"><span class="feat-icon" aria-hidden="true">💬</span> Chat Channels <span class="tag tag-live">Live</span> <span class="tag tag-addon">Add-on</span></div>
        <p>A chat widget styled to your site, plus Facebook, Instagram &amp; TikTok Messenger — one add-on, every chat channel. Same brain as your text line, answering pricing, hours, services, and booking wherever customers type.</p>
