      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-title"><span class="feat-icon" aria-hidden="true">📅</span> Built-In Calendar &amp; Booking <span class="tag tag-live">Live</span></div>
        <p>A complete scheduling system runs inside your front desk — your services, durations, prices, hours, and buffers. Customers book straight into it by text or chat, and it confirms on the spot.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-title"><span class="feat-icon" aria-hidden="true">👥</span> Team &amp; Multi-Staff Scheduling <span class="tag tag-live">Live</span></div>
        <p>Multiple staff, each with their own services, hours, and calendar. Round-robin to balance the load, or let customers pick their person — handled automatically.</p>
      </div>
