        <div class="feat-title"><span class="feat-icon" aria-hidden="true">🔀</span> Smart Lead Capture &amp; Routing <span class="tag tag-live">Live</span></div>
        <p>New inquiries from your website, Facebook, and Instagram get captured, sorted, and sent to the right person automatically — new bookings to the front, accounts to the office, everything else where it belongs. It all sits in one organized system instead of scattered across your phone, inbox, and DMs.</p>
